Start
User Choose:
   Display "Welcome to Ammamrɛ Online Footwear Showroom!"
   Display "Select an option:"
   Display "[1] Create Account"
   Display "[2] Login"
   Input choice
   
If choice is "1":
   Display "Please provide your information to create an account:"
   Input username
   Input password
   Create new account using provided username and password
   Display "Account successfully created. You are now logged in."

Login (with New Account):
   Display "Please enter your login credentials:"
   Input enteredUsername
   Input enteredPassword
   If enteredUsername and enteredPassword match a created account:
      Display "Login successful. Welcome back, username!"

Display Homepage:
   Display "Welcome to the Ammamrɛ Online Footwear Showroom!"
   Display "Explore our latest collection of trendy Nike sneakers."

Display Product Catalogue:
   Display "Browse through our wide selection of sneakers:"
   Display List of Sneaker Categories
   Input selectedCategory

Display Buy Tab:
   Display "Select your favorite sneakers:"
   Display List of Sneakers in selectedCategory
   Input selectedSneaker

Display Linked Store:
   Display "You've chosen [selectedSneaker]."
   Display "Click the link below to purchase directly:"
   Display Link to Purchase
End
